    <item>
      <title>随着下议院的签署，米莱改革计划将提交阿根廷参议院</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/milei-wins-key-lower-house-support-for-argentina-s-reforms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷下议院首先批准了哈维尔·米莱总统的综合法案和财政法案，先是全部批准，后来又部分批准，这是这位自由主义领导人的重大胜利，他的改革现在在参议院面临更激烈的斗争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/milei-wins-key-lower-house-support-for-argentina-s-reforms</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 15:32:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
